extendedInfo.description: Digi-Key's app for Android is the design engineer's passkey to one of the world's largest inventories of in-stock electronic components. With instant access to digikey.com, our application is designed to help you source the electronic components you need whether you're at work, at home, or anywhere in between! Features: - Search over 2 million products and place orders.- Get product specifications, datasheets and view product photos. - Use barcode technology to find parts and quickly receive shipments from packing lists.- View Digi-Key, manufacturer & supplier provided product and informational videos. - Create lists of parts using shopping carts. Make sure to use the Contact Us feature, or send a note to mobile@digikey.com, to tell us of your experience or let us know if you experience any issues.
